                        <item name="Description" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">Input 6 or 7 numbers. The first 3 should correspond to the x, y and z coordinates of the origin. The last 3 or 4 should be a 3D rotation expressed in Euler angles in degrees, axis angles in radians or quaternions.</item>
                        <item name="InstanceGuid" type_name="gh_guid" type_code="9">c601525d-f21c-4f09-a58e-a64551dc8a68</item>
                        <item name="Name" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">Numbers</item>
